{
  "stem": "15393.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then I promise you, we will both go back to the ghetto, we won't stay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It's just for three days, four days, two days, however long this lasts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "How can you even suggest such a thing to me, she said.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "How can you suggest?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know what that means?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That means it's a death penalty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "How could I?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I can't possibly and where would I put you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But my mother knew that she lived alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "She had no family, she lived alone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had a beautiful apartment, of course an ex-Jewish apartment, in a beautiful part of town which was confiscated for.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was an SS and police district only, and the house belonged to the SS and police, and she had an apartment in it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had an apartment there because at some point before, she had a friend, what we would call a boyfriend, if you like, who was a very high-ranking Gestapo man.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he got that apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was-- what is the word-- I mean, this was not given to him, but it was-- I'm missing the word.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had the right to choose whatever he liked in that particular time-- part of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he chose this apartment and it was in the SS and police district.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when they were together, she was there, too-- with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At some point, he was sent away from Lwow to Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from the way we understood it, he was heading a Jewish concentration camp in Holland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was his allocation there, and so he had to leave almost on the spur of the moment and he left her in that apartment.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, you might as well stay here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why would you look for anything else?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
